name: From Diaries of a Trippy Artist
description:
Saturday 1PM
Thought I will start working on my new piece today.
My recently met friend just called me, shouting "I'm coming to trip mate!"
Not sure what he means.
4PM
OMG! I'm so lost and yet so happy! Those colours! I love him!
7PM
Trying to paint but it proves to be a serious task, I wish you could see what I do!
